Jane teaches her friend JJ that we didn't evolve from monkeys, but were created with Love by God. Through engaging storytelling and lively songs, children will learn that they are fearfully and wonderfully made by a loving Creator, rather than descended from monkeys or evolution. Let's embark on an adventure of discovery and celebrate the beautiful truth that each child is a precious creation of God!
